articles.title: Venezuela government announces new congress chief, opposition denounces 'coup'
articles.description: Venezuelan state television on Sunday announced that dissident opposition legislator Luis Parra is the new head of the congress, a move the opposition denounced as a "parliamentary coup."
articles.content:
CARACAS (Reuters) - Venezuelan state television on Sunday announced that dissident opposition legislator Luis Parra is the new head of the congress, a move the opposition denounced as a “parliamentary coup.” 
Reporting by Caracas newsroom
